### Kai's Favorite Quote Movie
# NOTE: GET /chat has no interactive channel to ask for tool-call approval, so
# per the MCP client guidelines it now fails closed: any MCP tool call the
# model attempts here (e.g. get_kais_favorite_movie_quote) is refused rather
# than silently executed, and the model will explain it could not complete
# the request. Use the Angular chatbot's /api/chat/stream flow to see the
# actual approval dialog and a real answer.
GET http://localhost:8083/chat?message=From which movie is Kai's favorite quote?
Accept: application/json

---

### Kai's Favorite Quote
GET http://localhost:8083/chat?message=What is Kai's favorite quote?
Accept: application/json

---

### Kai's Favorite Quote Batman
GET http://localhost:8083/chat?message=Is Kai's favorite movie quote from Batman?
Accept: application/json
